	 * v2.0.0 - Updated the queryAsync() method to correctly handle situations where we're getting cached rather than live data, but have not specified a minimumEndpointCount or minimumResponsePercent. In this case, the method will now return the response immediately, rather than waiting for a condition that would only have been met if we were querying live data.
